replies.body:
Are you kidding me ?! AND I THOUGHT I WAS CRAZY ALL ALONG. Everytime it happened, I could swear I clicked on it. I even started to question my short time memory !

 {{sticker:zombie-brand-mindblown}}

Edit: I think this is a recurrent bug. It might be caused by a latency in the information sent or whatever because I just remember that sometime when I have to ban a champion, it can take more than 5 second for my ban (or my pick) to ''lock in'' properly.
